r `G`-representation `A`,\nthe periodic cochain complex\n`0 ⟶ Hom(k[G], A) --(- ∘ (ρ(g) - 𝟙))--> Hom(k[G], A) --(- ∘ N)--> Hom(k[G], A) ⟶ ...`\nis isomorphic as a complex in `ModuleCat k` to\n`0 ⟶ A --(ρ(g) - 𝟙)--> A --N--> A --(ρ(g) - 𝟙)--> A --N--> A ⟶ ...`. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/RepresentationTheory/Homological/GroupCohomology/FiniteCyclic.html#Rep.FiniteCyclicGroup.homResolutionIso","kind":"def","line":50,"name":"Rep.FiniteCyclicGroup.homResolutionIso","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/087469e24922b85cb737497c74556c7dacc01f22/Mathlib/RepresentationTheory/Homological/GroupCohomology/FiniteCyclic.lean#L50-L64"}}],"imports":["Init","Mathlib.RepresentationTheory.Homological.FiniteCyclic","Mathlib.RepresentationTheory.Homological.GroupCohomology.LowDegree"],"instances":[],"name":"Mathlib.RepresentationTheory.Homological.GroupCohomology.FiniteCyclic"}